data.text:
The following table lists all the 2-digit country codes used by WIPO. AppColl uses the same codes whenever the CountryCode field is shown.

The codes can also be used for task rule triggering events instead of the full country name. For example, a triggering event used in a task rule could use CountryCode contains "US" just as easily as using Country contains "United States".
